 8 日中午，民警将吴某传唤至辖区派出所，经讯问，吴某承认因为觉得周某平时影响了自己学习，所以想惩罚一下他，他们的登录账号和密码都差不多，自己便背着家长偷改了周某报的第一志愿，将其第一志愿改为位于报考志愿里中下游的一所院校，事后是十分惶恐。根据《中华人民共和国治安管理处罚法》第二十九条第（三）项规定，阜城警方依法对吴某作出行政拘留处罚。目前案件正在进一步办理中。河北衡水一男生篡改他人高考志愿被行拘"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-d34c6899c030d037e3e06f7d7e370078_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "13 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/471217744"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8InrbzyqKh5pghEAMaCDY2OTk0NTI1IPCNoYcGMDo47wtAHXIJNDcxMjE3NzQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1626012326.0553174", "card_id": "Q_470254637", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 133}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美国搞乱阿富汗，现在拍屁股就走了，未来的阿富汗会怎样？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "塔利班被定为恐怖组织，那为什美国撤军后，塔利班进攻的那么顺利？既然是恐怖组织为什么还是不断的有人加入？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-6c055538ecd666fc00a4813039dab3a7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "12 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/470254637"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8InrbzyqKh5pghEAMaCDY2NzgwNDk5II3bi4cGMBE4+wVAHnIJNDcwMjU0NjM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1626012326.0556676", "card_id": "Q_470069077", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 283}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "从目前的困局来看，滴滴会从美国退市吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "根据国家数字安全法，滴滴的数据安全似乎是个无解的死局。是不是它很快就会被私有化而从美国退市？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e9c2b6e983d61869c4525015a4901266_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "11 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/470069077"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8InrbzyqKh5pghEAMaCDY2NzM5MzYwIO3Bh4cGMCc4phNAH3IJNDcwMDY5MDc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": 